{"tid":1918672,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實今年立法會市民自己配票行唔行得通？","createTime":"2020-03-10T08:58:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-11T07:19:13.000Z","uid":117622,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"3f96e46b363adcf35afb282861db1f8807667237","tid":1918672,"uid":117622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T08:58:49.000Z","msg":"睇返區議會香港島選區係大約有<br />\n24萬票屬於黃票<br />\n21萬票屬於藍票<br />\n<br />\n再睇返上次立法會選舉<br />\n最高票係60000<br />\n如果今年香港島有4個民主派/自決出選<br />\n市民自己配票例如一家人4個就夾定<br />\n4個民主派各一票<br />\n唔夠4個屋企人就揾FD夾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n團結就成事！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n24萬票分4份每人應該都可以有6萬票<br />\n應該夠拎足4席？<br />\n<br />\n因為如果有2個出選人特別多票<br />\n分分鐘比港共21萬票完美配票KO<br />\n今年選舉真係要諗定攻略<br />\n<br />\n利申9up 可以狂屌<br />\n純粹今年唔想輸<br />\n想係宜家諗定攻略出大量文宣<br />\n香港人今年立法會一定要好似區議會咁全勝"},{"pid":"a482d23584a19a3a11fa811d64cd7c50d28f150c","tid":1918672,"uid":117622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T09:14:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff028cd954528d4f71024e21dbac1d7db7d8080c","tid":1918672,"uid":288348,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T09:16:05.000Z","msg":"身分證號碼配票<br />\n最尾1,2 號投 A<br />\n3,4號 投 B...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71d401de7a5bdcace0922c9dc4c34694b580c465","tid":1918672,"uid":1435,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T09:22:51.000Z","msg":"到時戴妖就出山配票啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n慌佢唔搞咩"},{"pid":"5a81989a68eaf8ba7d3dde06a4e386d37fe1b3c0","tid":1918672,"uid":188805,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T09:37:23.000Z","msg":"根票站配票，由民主派區議員/社區幹事指示投邊個<br />\n全香港人一齊玩統戰，統佢老母臭閪共慘黨"},{"pid":"37cf8e13ca3ff754caed59dc5b971c21bef92328","tid":1918672,"uid":117622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":